Companies shouldn’t profit at the expense of the health and safety of those on the front lines fighting the #COVID19 pandemic.

AZ AG Mark Brnovich needs to do more to stop medical supply vendors and manufacturers from price gouging.

@RepGregStanton and I told him so today: https://t.co/TuYEalJL82

Our warm climate in Arizona will not protect you from contracting #coronavirus. 

With so much misinformation spreading, it’s important to get your information from a trusted source. 

@WHO is busting this and other myths here: https://t.co/AjhTxofW3h https://t.co/bnO5pVfZDe
